.TH SINGINE-MODEL 1 "2026-03-13" "singine 0.2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
singine-model \- inspect Singine model objects and bridge surfaces
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B singine model
\fISUBCOMMAND\fR [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B model
command exposes a lightweight catalog of named Singine objects, reference data,
and Collibra bridge types for discovery and inspection.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
.B catalog
List bootstrappers, auth operations, master data, reference data, and entity families.
.TP
.B inspect \fINAME\fR
Show a detailed description of one named model object.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
singine model catalog
singine model catalog --json
singine model inspect code-table
singine model inspect "Business Term"
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR singine (1)
